    <item>
      <title>匈牙利选举结果：维克多·欧尔班承认失败并祝贺彼得·马扎尔</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/hungary-election-orban-magyar.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理欧尔班维克托在全球范围内激发了民粹主义运动，但他无法克服本国公民日益增长的不满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/hungary-election-orban-magyar.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2026 21:04:13 GMT</pubDate>
