    <item>
      <title>谁是彼得·马扎尔（Peter Magyar），推翻匈牙利欧尔班的人</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/who-peter-magyar-hungary-election-opposition-orban.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马扎尔在匈牙利选举中取得成功，很大程度上是由于公众对腐败的普遍愤怒以及对经济增长乏力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/12/world/europe/who-peter-magyar-hungary-election-opposition-orban.html</guid>
